Package: pokeWrapper
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper Package for Pokemon API 
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Eva Nguyen & Connor Lee
Description: An R wrapper for the Pokemon API. More information on the API at https://	
    pokeapi.co/. A data frame of the first 151 pokemons from Generation 1 is returned. The
    package has two functions available. The function, poke.filter(), returns a data frame 
    based on pokemons requested. The function, summary(), returns a data frame with 
    aggregates of pokemon counts and mean capture rate by habitat or type. 
Depends:
	httr,
	tidyverse,
	dplyr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
